"(1) (i) A dense, acrid mist hung over the lush hills of as dawn gave way to a sudden, oppressive silence. The air, usually fragrant with earth and tropical blooms, now carried an undercurrent of heat and the sharp tang of impending disaster. Zoe, a local resident drawn by the distant rumble, paused on a narrow dirt road, her breath quickening as the ground began to tremble beneath her feet.\n(2) (i) Within minutes, the sky above the village darkened with a low, rolling thunder. Lava fountains erupted from a fissure on the northern slopes of the volcano, spewing rivers of molten rock and ash into the air. The ground shuddered violently, sending loose soil and pebbles skittering across Zoe’s path. She shielded her eyes, watching in awe and fear as the eruption roared, painting the horizon with glowing embers and smoke. Kampong Cham Province. March 23, 2024.\n(3) (i) , standing mere yards from the churning vent, witnessed the raw power of the volcanic eruption unfold in real time. The roar of the explosion echoed in her ears, mingled with the hiss of superheated gas and the sharp snap of falling pumice. As the ash began to fall, blanketing the landscape in a gray shroud, Zoe felt a mix of terror and wonder, her mind racing to process the primal spectacle unfolding before her eyes. Zoe Brown. witnessed a volcanic eruption."